ActOther Than Statutory Authority
SubjectCooperation Agreement with the European Space Agency
PrecisOrder authorizing the Minister of Foreign Affairs to sign, or to delegate authority to sign, on behalf of the Government of Canada, subject to ratification, the Cooperation AGREEMENT between Canada and the European Space Agency. The Agreement will replace the one signed in 2000, which will continue to apply until the updated version is in force.
